description.text: Document with technical product data of the AGV provided by the manufacturer
Dokument mit technischen Produktdaten, das vom Hersteller bereitgestellt wird
Information about the AGV type and the vehicle's applications
Type of Kinematic of the AGV. The enumerations according VDA5050 "DIFF", "OMNI", "THREEWHEEL", "OTHER" can be used.
Class of the AGV. The enumeration according VDA5050 with "FORKLIFT", "CONVEYER", "TUGGER", "CARRIER", "OTHER" can be used.
Direction of traveling of the AGV, the enumeration "FORWARD", "BACKWARD", "OMNI-DIRECTIONAL" can be used.
Transportation pinciple of the AGV. The enumeration "LOADPULLING", "LOADCARRYING", "MIXED" can be used.
Type of the localization the AGV is using. The enumeration according VDA5050 with "NATURAL", "REFLECTOR", "RFID", "DMC", "SPOT", "GRID", "OTHER" can be used.
Type of navigation the AGV uses. The enumeration according VDA5050 with "PHYSICAL_LINE_GUIDED", "VIRTUAL_LINE_GUIDED", "AUTONOMOUS" can be used.
Special applications and usage sectors of the AGV, e.g. EMC environment, chemical industry, mining, clean rooms, refrigerated rooms, areas with explosion risk
Special capabilities and functions of the AGV
Extent of protection provided by an enclosure against access to hazardous parts, against ingress of solid foreign objects and against ingress of water

Technical properties related to the energy supply of the AGV
Type of auxiliary energy the AGV is consuming, the enumeration "POWER", "DIESEL", "GAS", "HYDROGEN", "HYBRID", "SOLAR", "OTHER" can be used
Way to absorb auxiliary energy. The enumeration "INDUCTION", "CONDUCTORRAIL", "FLEXIBLECABLE", "CHARGINGCABLE", "FILLER", "OTHER" can be used
Type of storage the AGV is using. The enumeration "BATTERY", "TANK", "CARTRIDGE", "CAPACITOR", "OTHER" can be used.
